A year ago I was able to compete for the first time. Hands down the best experience I’ve ever had. From hitting the gym, the diet, and finding the best suit I enjoyed the entire journey. I can’t wait to do it again this year! Thank @musclecontest for this experience. Grateful to my coach @pjclassic_ @flex_academy_inc and @illusionsbyaggie for helping me find the perfect suit I asked for. @wellness.cass.pro thank you for helping me with my posing and confidence for my first show.
Overall unforgettable experience.
